query:
SELECT
                MAX(id),
                SUM(value),
                COUNT(*)
            FROM
                tap_horizon_receipts
            WHERE
                collection_id = $1
                AND service_provider = $2
                AND payer = $3
                AND data_service = $4
                AND id <= $5
                AND signer_address IN (SELECT unnest($6::text[]))
                AND timestamp_ns > $7
